<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07825</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT ESTABLISHING THE NATIONAL COUNCIL FOR THE PRESERVATION OF MANGROVE FORESTS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to ensure the preservation, reforestation and sustainable development of the mangrove resources through the establishment of reservation areas exclusively for mangrove forests. Enumerates certain prohibited acts that may damage or destruct the mangrove forests and provides penalties for violations of such acts.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “The Mangrove Forest Protection and Preservation Act.” </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>NIETO, JOHN MARVIN &quot;YUL SERVO&quot; C., MACEDA, EDWARD VERA PEREZ, MARTINEZ, ERIC M., SANDOVAL, FEDERICO &quot;RICKY&quot; II S., MALAPITAN, DALE &quot;ALONG&quot; R., OLIVAREZ, ERIC L.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-05-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-08)</td><td>2. Silverio (000 2018-08-22)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON CLIMATE CHANGE ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>